{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fe26d5c8aa","title":"关于转发西南军区简报第四号的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"613f57b0a2","index":0,"year":1950,"month":11,"day":16,"articleId":"fe26d5c8aa"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"fa24faeffc","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"fe26d5c8aa","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邓，指邓子恢，当时任中国人民解放军中南军区第二政治委员。谭，指谭政，当时任中国人民解放军中南军区第三政治委员。赵，指赵尔陆，当时任中国人民解放军中南军区参谋长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"9e0ba01fc4","type":"title","text":"关于转发西南军区刺菲简报第四号的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"fe26d5c8aa"},{"id":"fa24faeffc","type":"paragraph","text":"华南分局及广东军区，广西省委及广西军区，并告邓、谭、赵”","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"fe26d5c8aa"},{"id":"70ea2e3d13","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将西南军区期简报第四号转发给你们作参考。西南军区对于期能工作极为认真，剩能中执行的各项政策亦是正确的，故取得了很大成绩。广西解放在西南之前而剩成绩则落在西南之后，为什么这样，请你们加以检讨并以结果告诉我们。我提议广西军区从十二月份起仿照西南办法每月发一次期通报，总结战绩，纠正缺点，务使全省汇患在几个月内基本解决。如何，盼复。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"fe26d5c8aa"},{"id":"0cd4e65d68","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"fe26d5c8aa"},{"id":"b57140d500","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月十六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"fe26d5c8aa"}],"page":{"id":"c7a323adbe","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"fe26d5c8aa","start":370,"end":370}}}},"__N_SSG":true}